summary: This document is an invoice from FedEx detailing transportation charges for services rendered on October 24, 2003. It includes information about discounts applied and payment due dates, along with references to account numbers and service types.
keyFacts: Total charges on the invoice amount to $24.04 after discounts.
The payment is due by November 5, 2003.
The document references multiple account numbers related to FedEx services.
